narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend: learning Spanish is so important, and this class makes it easy.
I would recommend the class as an easy introduction to Spanish. You can speak a surprising amount by the end but it's certainly not as intensive as it old be.
If you want to take spanish and don't know any, you must take L1.
